data.description: If you are looking for a Beautiful Home, Privacy, and Land, then look no further! Nestled in a great country location in fast growing Woodruff, and a short drive to Spartanburg and Greenville. This impressive property boasts  3420 sqft of luxurious living space in the main home with an additional 2216 finished sqft of second floor living space in the big red barn on the property.  Step into a world of elegance with 4 spacious bedrooms, 2 offices and a big bonus room that offers versatility for your needs. As you enter the foyer, two stunning columns open to the two story living room with breathtaking finishes and 20ft ceiling. The master bedroom boasts a tray ceiling, walk-in closet, and dual vanities. The heart of the home lies in the kitchen: revel in ample cabinet space, double wall oven and convenient center island with electric stove.  A set of double doors open to the beautiful covered back patio. Additionally, the paved circle driveway and 2-car covered carport provides easy access to the mudroom door and can serve as a great drop zone of your family needs. Every bedroom is thoughtfully crafted ensuring a harmonious blend of functionality and style throughout. Beautiful brick, stone accents and no HOA- come see it today!
